blog.name: littlenoona
blog.title: Noona.
blog.description: Too much smut for my own good - and I'm not even sorry.

summary: So, I just had a nap and I had the most fucked up dream, I’m telling you, listen to this(it’s in bits and pieces, like dreams...
body:
So, I just had a nap and I had the most fucked up dream, I’m telling you, listen to this(it’s in bits and pieces, like dreams usually are, but I’ll tell you what I remember). 

So the dreams starts off with me being on a boat, well more like a cruise that resembles the titanic(it might not be going where you think it’s going), so we’re going over this bridge thing, and all of a sudden there’s this loud ass bang, and the ship nosedives into the water, but no one is drowning because we’re all inside the ship and the glass is holding out the water and withstanding the pressure(dream logic), despite the fact that we are going deeper and deeper, literally landing on the bottom of the ocean. 

So on the bottom, there’s like a million other cruise ships, cars, petrol stations(?!) and small buildings, again, we’re completely fine because the water hasn’t come through the glass yet and it’s holding. 

Now I’m freaking the fuck out, because I can’t swim and going on boats and sinking is one of my biggest fears.

QUEUE FUCKING JUNGKOOK WALKING THROUGH THE DOOR. 

This dream has absolutely no talking in it, it’s all incoherent babbling but somehow my dreamself understands all of it?! 

Anyway, the entire population of the cruise keeps going about their daily business as if nothing had happened, literally eating food on the deck of the ship despite being thousands of feet below the surface, and not drowning(?). 

So we figure out that we’re kept here by some evil presence that’s trying to relay some message to us about Jim Carrey’s son(?!), who died, caused the mother to go insane and die and Jim Carrey to gain super powers, his power was to make people forget, erase memories ect. but obviously not soon enough to help his wife, and his eyes would always go ice cold blue whenever it happened. 

We try and find this presence that’s keep us here by literally (Jungkook) parkouring across other ships (I desperately try to follow, but he’s the fucking golden boy, who am I kidding). 

Finding this massive ship that looks rusty and crap (Kinda like the one from ‘Ghost Ship’ if you’ve seen that movie), we explore it and get to the cargo hold where we find this little kid (ghost of Carrey’s son) who’s talking to Jungkook, he’s freaking out and so am I. 

Exploring further into the basement we find this robot(imagine a female version of Ultron), who’s working on several different machines, ends up strapping the kid into this thing that looks like a surfing board and we run the fuck out of there. 

We go back to the others and try to explain the entire thing, but the glass of the ship starts cracking and isn’t going to hold much longer, queue me freaking the fuck out again because holy shit this is my worst nightmare. 

(I know there’s more bits of stuff with Jungkook, but I honestly don’t remember them that well other than seeing him standing around and making my legs feel like jelly)

And that was it?! Brain pls.

So the dreams starts off with me being on a boat, well more like a cruise that resembles the titanic(it might not be going where you think it’s going), so we’re going over this bridge thing, and all of a sudden there’s this loud ass bang, and the ship nosedives into the water, but no one is drowning because we’re all inside the ship and the glass is holding out the water and withstanding the pressure(dream logic), despite the fact that we are going deeper and deeper, literally landing on the bottom of the ocean. 

So on the bottom, there’s like a million other cruise ships, cars, petrol stations(?!) and small buildings, again, we’re completely fine because the water hasn’t come through the glass yet and it’s holding. 

Now I’m freaking the fuck out, because I can’t swim and going on boats and sinking is one of my biggest fears.

QUEUE FUCKING JUNGKOOK WALKING THROUGH THE DOOR. 

This dream has absolutely no talking in it, it’s all incoherent babbling but somehow my dreamself understands all of it?! 

Anyway, the entire population of the cruise keeps going about their daily business as if nothing had happened, literally eating food on the deck of the ship despite being thousands of feet below the surface, and not drowning(?). 

So we figure out that we’re kept here by some evil presence that’s trying to relay some message to us about Jim Carrey’s son(?!), who died, caused the mother to go insane and die and Jim Carrey to gain super powers, his power was to make people forget, erase memories ect. but obviously not soon enough to help his wife, and his eyes would always go ice cold blue whenever it happened. 

We try and find this presence that’s keep us here by literally (Jungkook) parkouring across other ships (I desperately try to follow, but he’s the fucking golden boy, who am I kidding). 

Finding this massive ship that looks rusty and crap (Kinda like the one from ‘Ghost Ship’ if you’ve seen that movie), we explore it and get to the cargo hold where we find this little kid (ghost of Carrey’s son) who’s talking to Jungkook, he’s freaking out and so am I. 

Exploring further into the basement we find this robot(imagine a female version of Ultron), who’s working on several different machines, ends up strapping the kid into this thing that looks like a surfing board and we run the fuck out of there. 

We go back to the others and try to explain the entire thing, but the glass of the ship starts cracking and isn’t going to hold much longer, queue me freaking the fuck out again because holy shit this is my worst nightmare. 

(I know there’s more bits of stuff with Jungkook, but I honestly don’t remember them that well other than seeing him standing around and making my legs feel like jelly)

And that was it?! Brain pls.

body:
So earlier I was getting changed after work and I heard the big hit intro thing and I’m like GASP??? and ran downstairs to find my stepdad had put on Boy With Luv. He said he wanted to see what the fuss was about.

Anyway he’s watching and he goes “Oh she’s pretty.” And I’m like sir that is my boy Park Jimin and he’s like “Oh. Well he’s just lovely.”

Anyway he realized during the chorus that he knew the song because him and the dude he drives to work with were listening to it on the radio on their way to the job and he was pleasantly surprised and he said “You should sell your BTS tickets…to me.” And I told him to go fuck himself.
